---

**Core Network Functions:**

| Component | Function |
|-----------|----------|
| **gNB** | 5G base station, connects UE to core via radio link |
| **AMF** | First point of contact, handles registration and mobility |
| **AUSF** | Authenticates the user (verifies identity) |
| **SMF** | Sets up data sessions, assigns IP addresses |
| **UDM** | Stores subscription data (who you are, what you can access) |
| **PCF** | Applies policies (QoS rules, charging) |
| **UPF** | Forwards actual user data to the internet |
| **NSSF** | Selects the right network slice for the service |
